---
import Container from "../../primitives/Container.astro";
---
<section class="bg-white" aria-labelledby="hydrogen-intro-title">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Powering the next phase of the energy transition</p>
      <h2 id="hydrogen-intro-title" class="fluid-h2 mt-3">Turning surplus solar into industrial-scale clean fuel.</h2>
      <p class="fluid-lead mt-5 text-muted">
        Empereal designs, supplies, and commissions turnkey green hydrogen systems that couple directly with solar PV and wind generation — converting surplus renewable energy into high-purity hydrogen for industrial decarbonization, heavy transport, and the wider clean fuel ecosystem.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
